sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant TitleBar
    participant OSToggleButton
    participant AgentOSContext
    participant Index
    participant AgentOSDesktop
    participant DockBar
    participant WindowManager
    participant Window

    Note over User,Window: === 模式切换：经典 → OS ===

    User->>TitleBar: 点击 OS 模式按钮
    TitleBar->>OSToggleButton: onClick()
    OSToggleButton->>AgentOSContext: toggleOSMode()
    AgentOSContext->>AgentOSContext: dispatch TOGGLE_OS_MODE
    AgentOSContext-->>Index: re-render (isOSMode=true)
    Index->>AgentOSDesktop: 渲染桌面

    Note over User,Window: === 打开窗口 ===

    User->>DockBar: 点击 Dock 图标
    DockBar->>AgentOSContext: openWindow(type, title)
    alt 窗口已存在
        AgentOSContext->>AgentOSContext: focusWindow(id) + 恢复最小化
    else 窗口不存在
        AgentOSContext->>AgentOSContext: 创建新窗口 (居中 800×500)
    end
    AgentOSContext-->>WindowManager: re-render windows[]
    WindowManager->>Window: 渲染 Window 组件
    Window->>Window: 懒加载页面 + 定位

    Note over User,Window: === 拖拽窗口 ===

    User->>Window: mousedown 标题栏
    Window->>Window: startDrag(id, e)
    loop 拖拽中
        User->>Window: mousemove
        Window->>Window: 本地更新位置 (optimistic)
    end
    User->>Window: mouseup
    Window->>AgentOSContext: moveWindow(id, x, y)

    Note over User,Window: === 聚焦窗口 ===

    User->>Window: click 窗口
    Window->>AgentOSContext: focusWindow(id)
    AgentOSContext->>AgentOSContext: zIndex = nextZIndex++

    Note over User,Window: === 关闭窗口 ===

    User->>Window: 点击红色关闭按钮
    Window->>AgentOSContext: closeWindow(id)
    AgentOSContext->>AgentOSContext: 过滤窗口 + 聚焦最高层

    Note over User,Window: === 模式切换：OS → 经典 ===

    User->>TitleBar: 再次点击 OS 模式按钮
    TitleBar->>OSToggleButton: onClick()
    OSToggleButton->>AgentOSContext: toggleOSMode()
    AgentOSContext->>AgentOSContext: dispatch TOGGLE_OS_MODE
    AgentOSContext-->>Index: re-render (isOSMode=false)
    Index->>Index: 渲染经典布局 (Sidebar + TabBar + Content)
    Note right of Index: tabs 状态完全保留
